ectly. It's kind of a technical puzzle, but I’m curious about how it all fits together. I'll dive into the specifics of the classpath settings and how they interact with the Hadoop build process.\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0832257ffadd7b600169fe5d2a25008190bebef46afc987ec5\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp_l0rmmg6h0-y0t2l6SWcOoBr3u5JmBrTwP3vqY4ct_VM-_YQyW8ozqeat_ZID4khc67n2n86o0MtusOFsftq8k6wWEK8oRSWfzRJa5BZv4KlE5vMDJbxBVeJH1d5JmzQE1Wn08mOfDr6gSa7J-5_RK7I6yaqKeC4MHwq3ZIapMGI-OzyRBioqhK14Kzam9fuwMQsR-YgZRMi0pVgfnN7ok-bDOVTAK0WiwN2N_hsnK6SkGDH1iaNv97t9JqW5XB9jaBfmeYCwUO4MWXm6K0Bvc9hGL68xD558QmSdRjXKXpWLJuEPAqXIKi9xfuDXvedf4whM4BRNSTyEm4uwjtpqAX3Qssw9BkQkhaUkkBQ3T2-x4LmUE2qaM8qFxVzmoFpfEts83-_CSGAu7wHC1x5cs1199u6a0-2WFiJFog0lp4lKNRuBH2wsLrdSDgtR3CRGtjsXdZENkpSG_9HuhsA0MW4_qJ9N3_QMdrgx--t6a7gVms5V_U_fZFV56m8ud9Q3ThLul7UhPeFuijBjeW2WZ5G4F2qGi0YsveZnB6tPJu3BYmOB46AM7JYebQMsT8wEwkj_bYFY8ldTkoC3riDEnA7PfsRX6GB7KQcv-uSsmLp0aVG9FxY0I_zNf0008M3wOwlivwMl-sHiaw1fMMI13jPcf34MvL-eeqVf6Pu49eRlfP7LvoFQVbcfK2eS-6mNkuTsgRMdI6JWB8q7u8h-lGIO9ye32a2-EwcBe4ZuUeqZ72oW64zHWGV6g-XoAZ7yTqpnyIaEqOs_A91yJiLsKOXnDYHZGxdM1VAr01lbNcS3HVWW8RY1dN8wIdxS7fQ1kTDDn7vx9ZcXj2QshemPVIanCnKS4zfWTOjNKYJmlbxVIBJVnvAO1lhgBhrO4hvq3Qh_jzERa1n6v1chT_lPNsdDrjgZNY7YRnHWZC6zbSDniW0NV7WV4wyBrkuxC5TzzyGkhxsWANqXEj1s0GmB4wtbwIuvz9RYAtFSmlZ3LK_qcc=\\\",\\\"summary\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"summary_text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"**Checking Hadoop configuration**\\\\n\\\\nI'm considering building and resolving the newest version of Hadoop. I wonder if the issue relates to the classpath. It feels like there's a potential connection there. I'll need to explore that further and make sure everything aligns correctly. It's kind of a technical puzzle, but I’m curious about how it all fits together. I'll dive into the specifics of the classpath settings and how they interact with the Hadoop build process.\\\"}]}\"}, {\"type\": \"toolCall\", \"id\": \"call_6lkJmLrpI6bXaUy2z9G0eJ